My email | My linkedin Page

September 2017 - June 2021 Idaho Falls, Idaho
• Notable classes include: AP Physics, AP US History, AP Calculus, College-Level trigonometry, AP Government

August 2021 - August 2023 Rio de Janeiro, Brazil
Representative The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-Day Saints Rio de Janeiro
• Led weekly trainings of 8-10 volunteers to revamp communication with others, goal settings and following up on plans • Persevered through long days of work • De-escalated difficult interactions in a professional manner • Collaborated with volunteers on weekly and monthly progress



• The Eagle Scout Award



Collaborative, Bilingual (Portuguese), and Goal-oriented



• QPR Certification • CPR Certification • RBT Certification/40hr Course • MANDT Certification
